{"tid":1809223,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何以...完 林海峰叱咤表演片段","createTime":"2020-01-03T02:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T06:09:27.000Z","uid":282677,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f58e62826bd47d164d0a996b360173578b362be","tid":1809223,"uid":282677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"何以‧完 Jan林海峰表演片段<br />\n每年叱咤最令人期待嘅環節，一定係林海峰嘅表演，而今年阿Jan純粹「聲音導航」，但每句旁白、字幕「直入人心」：每一句都以「何以」開頭，反問觀眾連串問題，內容有意思得嚟仲有幾個感動位，例如反問觀眾今年叱咤點解要轉形式搞？投票點解變得咁重要？仲講咗好多呢半年香港見到嘅畫面，例如喺商場唱歌仲流行過喺k房等等。<br />\n<br />\n//何以你今晚會安坐家中睇叱咤？<br />\n何以今年嘅叱咤一個現場觀眾都冇？<br />\n何以過往嘅叱咤現場投票會變成今年嘅網上投票？<br />\n何以你每年實睇嘅頒獎禮，今年會冇咗個實體頒獎禮？<br />\n何以一人一票喺呢個地方係變得越來越矜貴？<br />\n何以明明千載不變嘅音樂肯定，最後個獎座會落喺一堆垃圾裏面？<br />\n何以今年有咁多場大大小小嘅演唱會都要一一取消？<br />\n何以有人話要放棄一代年青人，但係花姐就要一手湊大Mirror一班年青人，仲要將佢哋培育到入圍我最喜愛組合？<br />\n何以屯門公園嘅娜娜歌精舞勁，肥媽首歌唱到街知巷聞，但係佢哋就冇入圍我最喜愛女<br />\n歌手最後五強？<br />\n何以有人敢唱人話，但係就有人唔肯講人話？<br />\n何以今年去商場唱歌係流行過去K房唱歌？<br />\n何以一首廣東歌可以令你感動、安慰、鼓舞、落淚，甚至係會恐懼？<br />\n何以你可以將你曾經最喜愛歌手嘅唱片打爛變成碎片？<br />\n我哋嘅樂壇何以為繼？<br />\n2019 何以 完<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n2020 和你投//<br />\n<a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/detail.php?item=5e0c1abbf294e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fitem%3D5e0c1abbf294e&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7PcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=6550a0d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/detail.php?item=5e0c1abbf294e</a>"},{"pid":"3f8d39c154f96cb48f9867c36129157168bfb9bf","tid":1809223,"uid":282677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的組合、叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的女歌手、叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的歌曲<br />\n叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的組合：RubberBand<br />\n叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的女歌手:方皓玟<br />\n叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的歌曲:人話<br />\n<a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/detail.php?item=5e09c39f8e910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fitem%3D5e09c39f8e910&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7PcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=f9710fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/detail.php?item=5e09c39f8e910</a>"},{"pid":"2dcaa56ba4ad1d979661b3e939d37a7d120546c0","tid":1809223,"uid":282677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"叱咤樂壇我最喜愛 五強單位表演：(RubberBand x 方皓玟) - 未來見 ＋ 人話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/detail.php?item=5e0cca05a02f6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fitem%3D5e0cca05a02f6&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7PcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=80ba5c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/detail.php?item=5e0cca05a02f6</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"5255f7d81d8c40555ab720126384043129039117","tid":1809223,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"ok幾高質，推一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2c3858716adebd5abae416b6378ea633692370","tid":1809223,"uid":106348,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:54:59.000Z","msg":"曾經有段片係剪接子華神同老豆都無飛去串林狗<br />\n但呢刻真心 respect 林海峰"},{"pid":"000f952247a76a4bde0e6215d688a730b18187a2","tid":1809223,"uid":110018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"respect<br />\n<br />\n呢段真係好精彩"},{"pid":"dbedde7e47946ff745eab641282bcee0cc785b58","tid":1809223,"uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"子華呢?"},{"pid":"d9f1dfa95463efb802ac0a6dd89fd3c5d258ecdb","tid":1809223,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"何以完"},{"pid":"a33c8bd85bfce2df0c08cfb9209509b0451e248f","tid":1809223,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbedde7e47946ff745eab641282bcee0cc785b58","tid":1809223,"uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"子華呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"去咗支那拍賀碎片"}]}